WhisperKit model directory.

This folder is intentionally checked in empty (via this .gitkeep). Real model
files (~1.6GB for whisper-large-v3-turbo) are NOT committed — run
`scripts/fetch-whisperkit-model.sh` once before building for device to
populate this directory.

The CSVMirror / Voice subsystems will refuse to lazy-download at runtime
(implementation-addendum §4 hard reject #15). If this directory is empty at
launch, `VoiceCaptureService.initializeIfNeeded()` returns readiness
`.unavailable(.modelMissing(...))` and the UI disables the mic button.
